com.esri.mo2.map.dpy
Interface Element

All Superinterfaces:
Cloneable, Data, Element, Identifiable, MapData, Spatial
All Known Implementing Classes:
BaseElement
public interface Element
extends Element

A a visual object that can be displayed in a GraphicsLayer. Note: If you modify the underlying geometry directly, you must also call invalidate() to ensure the geometry changes are noticed by the underlying memory Dataset. See Element.invalidate() for details.
